    {
      "type": "drop",
      "text": "Top row sits right above home. R and T are left-index reaches, U and Y are right-index reaches, E and I are middle-finger reaches. The move is the same every time: reach up, tap, snap straight back home. Keep your anchors on F and J."
    },
    {
      "type": "callout",
      "icon": "⬆️",
      "title": "Up and back, every time",
      "text": "Don't look down to find the top row - your finger knows the way. Reach, tap, return. If your hand floats away from home, you're done for. Anchor first, reach second."
    },
